#### Authorizations

HTTPBasicHTTPBearerHTTPBasicHTTPBearer

​

Authorization

string

header

required

Basic authentication header of the form `Basic <encoded-value>`, where `<encoded-value>` is the base64-encoded string `username:password`.

#### Body

application/json

​

project_id

string

required

The ID of the project

Example:

`"my_entity/my_project"`

​

digests

string[] | null

The digests of the tables to query

Example:

`"aonareimsvtl13apimtalpa4435rpmgnaemrpgmarltarstaorsnte134avrims"`

​

include_storage_size

boolean | null

default:false

If true, the `storage_size_bytes` column is returned.

#### Response

Successful Response

​

tables

TableStatsRow · object[]

required

Show child attributes

